Thank you all for the valuable input.  I was more just curious if it was possible.  I just hit 49, and am a pretty damn good tank if I do say so myself.<br>
<br>
I do realize that stats are useful but also some just eye candy.  Right now, at 49, I have unbuffed (except for minor shielding and kunzar strength - thanks cobalt) 2100 hps, 900 AC, and 900 ATK.  My strength is about 145, stamina around 120, dex at about 110 (just picked up a Cloak of Shadows recently), and agi somewhere just over 100.<br>
<br>
I generally don't have much trouble holding agro unless the pally I regurlarly group with over agros too soon.  Spells are a pain to keep up with.<br>
<br>
Again, didn't want to start a huge debate over the necessity of race or whatnot.  I'm proud to be a human warrior, and hope to hit 60 eventually and be IP II IIVII IP  =)<br>
